OL,3,CShoplifting hits 'epidemic levels' as
OL,4,Cworkers fear for their safety
OL,6,FThe increase is having an impact on
OL,7,Fboth businesses and their employees,
OL,8,Fand there are fears police are no
OL,9,Flonger able to help tackle the problem.
OL,11,FFiona Malone, who owns Tenby Stores in
OL,12,Fthe centre of the Pembrokeshire town,
OL,13,Fsaid she is experiencing unprecedented
OL,14,Flevels of theft.
OL,16,F"Certainly we've noticed our losses
OL,17,Fdramatically increase," she told ITV's
OL,18,FWales This Week.
