OL,6,F"We looked at it last year and we were
OL,7,Flooking at about #26,000 of losses.
OL,8,FThat's a huge amount because we are a
OL,9,Fsmall shop.
OL,11,F"Sometimes, I've been told (by police)
OL,12,F'it was only #10'. But, if all of our
OL,13,Fcustomers took #10 worth of goods we
OL,14,Fwouldn't stay in business for longer
OL,15,Fthan three months."
OL,17,FWales has seen the sharpest increase
OL,18,Fin shoplifting of the four UK nations,
OL,19,Fand the uplift has coincided with
OL,20,Fthose working in the sector
OL,21,Fexperiencing violence and abuse.
