OL,3,CShoplifting hits 'epidemic levels' as
OL,4,Cworkers fear for their safety
OL,6,F- the union which represents retail
OL,7,Fworkers - 70% of respondents said they
OL,8,Fhad experienced verbal abuse at work
OL,9,Fin the last year, while almost one in
OL,10,Ffive said they had been physically
OL,11,Fassaulted.
OL,13,FOne retail worker, who wished to
OL,14,Fremain anonymous, said: "They show us
OL,15,F(what they are stealing) and say 'you
OL,16,Fcan't do anything, you can't touch me,
OL,17,FI'm taking it'.
