OL,6,F"They also abuse (us) a lot, verbally,
OL,7,Feven sometimes physically. They throw
OL,8,Fbottles, they swear, they use abusive
OL,9,Fwords, sometimes they are even racist.
OL,11,F"Sometimes they threaten 'we'll see
OL,12,Fyou outside'. A lot of the time our
OL,13,Fshift starts quite early in the
OL,14,Fmorning or late at night, so sometimes
OL,15,Fit's really unsafe.
OL,17,F"A few women in our company changed
OL,18,Ftheir shifts because they don't want
OL,19,Fto work late because they've been
OL,20,Fthreatened."
