OL,3,CShoplifting hits 'epidemic levels' as
OL,4,Cworkers fear for their safety
OL,6,FPolice forces across Wales say they
OL,7,Fare prioritising shoplifting where
OL,8,Fthey can.
OL,10,FHowever, they say the approach has
OL,11,Fchanged, with a growing focus on the
OL,12,Fcauses and its prevention.
OL,14,FNorth Wales Police have been running
OL,15,Fan intervention campaign which has
OL,16,Fseen a 9% increase in the detection
OL,17,Frate for shoplifting
