OL,3,CShoplifting hits 'epidemic levels' as
OL,4,Cworkers fear for their safety
OL,6,FSuperintendent Jonathan Bowcott said
OL,7,Fhe believes some of the criticism of
OL,8,Fpolice response to an increase in
OL,9,Fshoplifting reports "is probably fair".
OL,11,F"We really are committed to improving
OL,12,Fthings across the country in relation
OL,13,Fto this," he continued.
OL,15,F"It does have an impact on society
OL,16,Fthat we understand better now than I
OL,17,Fthink we have in the past.
OL,19,F"In policing we prioritise things on
OL,20,Fthe threat harm and risk that they
OL,21,Fcause to our communities.
