OL,6,F"We will prioritise attendance where
OL,7,Fsomeone has been detained, perhaps by
OL,8,Fsecurity, or when someone has used and
OL,9,Fthreatened violence.
OL,11,F"Dealing with the persistent nature of
OL,12,Fsome offenders, and the circumstances
OL,13,Fthat cause them to offend, is a real
OL,14,Fchallenge."
OL,16,FTheft cost UK retailers #1.8billion
OL,17,Flast year, with many businesses having
OL,18,Fto cover the losses themselves.
