OL,3,CShoplifting hits 'epidemic levels' as
OL,4,Cworkers fear for their safety
OL,6,FSara Jones, director of the Welsh
OL,7,FRetail Consortium, said: "The more
OL,8,Fmoney retailers have to cover
OL,9,Fthemselves, the less money they have
OL,10,Favailable to keep prices down for the
OL,11,Fcustomer.
OL,13,F"I think the challenge is there's a
OL,14,Fperception among those involved in
OL,15,Fthis kind of behaviour that the
OL,16,Foffence won't be followed up, they
OL,17,Fwon't get prosecuted.
