OL,6,F"We need to see more at a UK
OL,7,FGovernment level, with policing not
OL,8,Fbeing devolved we need to see a
OL,9,Fstandalone offence for the protection
OL,10,Fof shop workers from violence and
OL,11,Fabuse in the workplace."
OL,13,FPolicing in Wales falls under the
OL,14,Fresponsibility of the UK Government's
OL,15,FHome Office.
